snippet.title: Asemblance: Oversight – Release Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
You are part of a team of scientists and engineers charged with using a classified technology to aid in recreating the human mind. Your success relies on unraveling the truth surrounding the origins of this strange technology, and outsmarting the ones who will do anything to keep it secret.

“Asemblance: Oversight” is a first-person exploration and puzzle-based game. 

http://www.asemblance.com/
